title: Sip or Spill: Moe Has A Few Tough Decisions To Make!
description:
Last week during Sip or Spill Kristin drank a rather innovative concoction when asked how much she makes.
This week it's Moe's turn, and he's got cups filled with 1 Raw egg, ranch, syrup, ketchup, and a double shot of expresso to get him through the morning.
